recipe.title: BlueBerry Muffins
recipe.instructions: Mix all the ingredients till soft dough, then put the dough in a muffin tray

recipe.title: Cheese Burgers
recipe.instructions: Grill the beef patties,  cut your onions, while grilling the beef patty put the cheese on top of the beef patty so that it can melt, then put all the ingredients together

recipe.title: Salmon Dish
recipe.instructions: Pour olive oil in a frying pan and put it on the stove,  season your salmon with spices,  fry your salmon for 10 mins,  pour some lemon juice on top of the salmon
